Q1: What is the relative influence of water and/or nutrient availability on tropical dry forest seedling growth and biomass allocation

Load models

models_q1 <- readRDS("./processed_data/models_q1.RData")
names(models_q1)
[1] "root_shoot_ratio_log" "total_biomass"        "rgr"

ANOVAs

models_q1 %>%

    # Remove traits and mass fractions models
    purrr::list_modify("agr_log" = NULL, "agr" = NULL) %>%
    anova_table_tidy(., model_list = T)

Post-Hoc

Total Biomass

total_biomass_emmeans <- emmeans(models_q1$total_biomass,
                                specs = ~nfixer*treatment)
total_biomass_emmeans
 nfixer   treatment            emmean   SE   df lower.CL upper.CL
 nonfixer no_additions           5.87 1.19 6.90     3.06     8.69
 fixer    no_additions           8.19 1.54 7.07     4.56    11.82
 nonfixer plus_nutrients         7.83 1.20 7.18     5.01    10.65
 fixer    plus_nutrients        13.76 1.56 7.52    10.11    17.40
 nonfixer plus_water             6.79 1.20 7.23     3.97     9.60
 fixer    plus_water            10.82 1.54 7.08     7.19    14.46
 nonfixer plus_water_nutrients   8.19 1.18 6.89     5.38    11.00
 fixer    plus_water_nutrients  13.77 1.55 7.14    10.13    17.41

Degrees-of-freedom method: kenward-roger 
Confidence level used: 0.95 
# Code the emmean position. For example the (0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0) means that
# fixer_plus_nutrients emmean is in the 4th row.

nonfixer_no_additions =   c(1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0)
fixer_no_additions   =    c(0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0)

nonfixer_plus_nutrients = c(0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0)
fixer_plus_nutrients  =   c(0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0)

nonfixer_plus_water =     c(0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0)
fixer_plus_water =        c(0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0)

nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients =  c(0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0)
fixer_plus_water_nutrients =     c(0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1)
data.frame(contrast(total_biomass_emmeans, method = list(

            # Comparisons between nfixer-nonfixer
            "fixer_no_additions-nonfixer_no_additions" = fixer_no_additions - nonfixer_no_additions,
            "fixer_plus_nutrients-nonfixer_plus_nutrients" = fixer_plus_nutrients - nonfixer_plus_nutrients,
            "fixer_plus_water-nonfixer_plus_water" = fixer_plus_water - nonfixer_plus_water,
            "fixer_plus_water_nutrients-nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients" = fixer_plus_water_nutrients - nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients,

            # Comparisons within nfixer
            "fixer_no_additions-fixer_plus_nutrients" = fixer_no_additions - fixer_plus_nutrients,
            "fixer_no_additions-fixer_plus_water" =     fixer_no_additions - fixer_plus_water,
            "fixer_no_additions-fixer_plus_water_nutrients" = fixer_no_additions - fixer_plus_water_nutrients,

            "fixer_plus_nutrients-fixer_plus_water" = fixer_plus_nutrients - fixer_plus_water,
            "fixer_plus_nutrients-fixer_plus_water_nutrients" = fixer_plus_nutrients - fixer_plus_water_nutrients,

            "fixer_plus_water-fixer_plus_water_nutrients" = fixer_plus_water - fixer_plus_water_nutrients,

            # Comparisons within nonfixer
            "nonfixer_no_additions-nonfixer_plus_nutrients" = nonfixer_no_additions - nonfixer_plus_nutrients,
            "nonfixer_no_additions-nonfixer_plus_water" =     nonfixer_no_additions - nonfixer_plus_water,
            "nonfixer_no_additions-nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients" = nonfixer_no_additions - nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients,

            "nonfixer_plus_nutrients-nonfixer_plus_water" = nonfixer_plus_nutrients - nonfixer_plus_water,
            "nonfixer_plus_nutrients-nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients" = nonfixer_plus_nutrients - nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients,

            "nonfixer_plus_water-nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients" = nonfixer_plus_water - nonfixer_plus_water_nutrients))) %>%

          dplyr::select(!c(SE, df)) %>%
          mutate(across(where(is.numeric), round, 12)) %>%
          clean_names() %>%
          reactable()

Plots Biomass and growth boxplot

# Get predictions
string <- c("models_q1")

data_pred_biomass_growth <-

        # Get models prediction
        gather_predictions(data_for_models,

                           # Return predictions of:
                            models_q1$rgr,
                            models_q1$total_biomass,
                            models_q1$root_shoot_ratio_log)  %>%

            # Get fitted values
            pivot_wider(names_from = model, values_from = pred) %>%
             rename_all(
              funs(

                # rename columns
                stringr::str_to_lower(.) %>%

                # Remove string from name and replace it with pred_
                stringr::str_replace(., c(string), "pred_") %>%

                # Remove dollar sing
                gsub("\\$", "", .))) %>%

        # Back transform log variables
        mutate(pred_root_shoot_ratio = exp(pred_root_shoot_ratio_log)) %>%

        # Select only pred variables
        dplyr::select(-c(init_height, pred_root_shoot_ratio_log))
# Generate plot combinations
vars_q1 <-
  crossing(

    # Get all numeric variables to plot (all y)
    as_tibble(t(combn(dplyr::select(data_pred_biomass_growth, where(is.numeric)) %>% names, 1))),

    # Select factor variables to plot
    x_axis_var = dplyr::select(data_pred_biomass_growth, nfixer) %>%  names,
    group_var = dplyr::select(data_pred_biomass_growth, treatment) %>%  names)
par(mfrow = c(2,2))
vars_q1 %>%
      # Gererate plots
      pmap( ~boxplot_plot_pmap(data = data_pred_biomass_growth,
                                y = !!sym(..1), x = !!sym(..2),
                                fill = !!sym(..3)))
